	explode lleg type FALL | SMOKE | FIRE | EXPLODE_ON_HIT | BITMAP2;
	explode rleg type FALL | SMOKE | FIRE | EXPLODE_ON_HIT | BITMAP2;
	explode flare1 type FALL | SMOKE | FIRE | BITMAP3;
